- ✅ `[GeneratedRegex]` used for 3 core patterns with proper `#if` fallback
- ✅ `IsAllUpperCase` uses `foreach` loop instead of LINQ `.All()`
- ✅ `IsAsciiAlphanumeric` uses `foreach` with early exit
- ✅ `Slugify` uses `ToLowerInvariant()` correctly
- ✅ `WordCount` is allocation-free with manual state machine

